<p>Normal, Consolidated, Kiosk these are case sensitive values. Example: [C=
DATA[Document.Type =3D "Normal"]] . If you tried to use the Kiosk value, th=
e cart still won't stop in PR workflow. Kiosk requisition type will always =
go straight to Po workflow. However, if you use this same object in Po work=
flow, you can get the PO to stop in a step/activity/folder.</p></td>
