<p>A set of all distinct values in this requisition for the specified field=
. The value is included in the set if the budget for this custom field valu=
e has been exceeded. (Related to original Budget feature, license "Budget".=
 This has no connection to the Budget Manager feature, license "Budget Mana=
ger", introduced in 19.1)</p></td>
