<p>12.2</p></td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>InvoiceIsValid</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>true/false</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Retruns true if the invoice has valid configuration</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>12.2</p></td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>UnmatchedForNeedsReceipt</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>true/false</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>True, if matching needs receipts</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>12.3</p></td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>UnmatchedForOverInvoiced</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>true/false</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><br></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>12.3</p></td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>IsBannerBudgetExceeded</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>true/false</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Returns true if any of the associated PO(s) has "BannerBudgetExceed" wor=
kflow warning flag. For use in orgs with Banner integration.</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>13.1</p></td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>IsBudgetAuthFailure</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>true/false</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Returns true if there is not enough budget for the invoice. The budget c=
heck is done through SCTInvoiceBudgetAuthRobot workflow step and it checks =
against banner.</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>13.3</p></td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Document.AccountNumber</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>string</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Returns supplier account number from the invoice document.</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>13.1</p></td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">HasInactiveCFValue</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">true/false</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Checks all the custom fields on the document to =
see if any have values that are inactive. Returns True if any one value is =
inactive. (Ex: <span class=3D"error">Document.HasInactiveCFValue =3D=3D tru=
e</span>)</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">14.1</td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">POTax1</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><span>Number (2 decimals, US format)</span></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Returns PO header-level Tax 1 value (e.g. Docume=
nt.POTax1 &gt; 0)</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">14.1</td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">POTax2</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><span>Number (2 decimals, US format)</span></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><span>Returns PO header-level Tax 2 value <span>=
(e.g. Document.POTax2 &gt; 0)</span> </span></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">14.1</td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">ContainAnyCanceledPOs</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">true/false</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Returns true if invoice contains one or more can=
celed POs (Ex:
<p>Document.ContainAnyCanceledPOs =3D=3D true)</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">14.2</td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">InvoiceContractBudgetHasExceeded</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">true/false</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">If contract has "Enforce Budget" flag checked an=
d budget is greater than zero, can route the document to an approval folder=
 if the invoice amount for a contract plus current invoice spend will resul=
t in the contract budget being exceeded.</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">14.2</td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">ContainAnyInvalidContract</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">true/false</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Returns true if a contract assigned to&nbsp;a in=
voice&nbsp;is not applicable. &nbsp;For example if the contract is no longe=
r usable, an invalid fulfillment center is used, or the contract is used on=
 a non-applicable catalog item. (Example usage: Document.ContainAnyInvalidC=
ontract =3D=3D true)</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">14.2</td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><span class=3D"legacy-color-text-d=
efault">InvoiceSalesTaxDiscrepancy</span></td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Number (2 decimals, US format)</p></td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>This should only be used after a workflow step using <span class=3D"lega=
cy-color-text-default">GetTaxEngineValueRobot. It should also only be used =
when&nbsp;tax engine integration is enabled.&nbsp;</span> <br>
Returns the value of the Tax Discrepancy value of a buyer invoice, which sh=
ows the difference between the tax provided by supplier and sales tax provi=
ded by Tax Engine values. Updated in 23.2 to also show difference between t=
he current invoice tax and sales tax provided by Tax Engine values (when Ta=
x Validation feature is enabled).<br>
(Ex: Document.<span class=3D"legacy-color-text-default">InvoiceSalesTaxDisc=
repancy</span>&gt; 10.00)</p></td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd">14.3</td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><span class=3D"legacy-color-text-d=
efault">InvoiceUseTaxDiscrepancy</span></td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd">Number (2 decimals, US format)</td=
>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd">This should only be used after a w=
orkflow step using <span class=3D"legacy-color-text-default">GetTaxEngineVa=
lueRobot. It should also only be used when&nbsp;tax engine integration is e=
nabled.&nbsp;</span> <br>
Returns the value of the Use Tax Discrepancy value of a buyer invoice, whic=
h shows the difference between the initial use tax and actual the use tax.<=
br>
(Ex: Document.<span class=3D"legacy-color-text-default">InvoiceUseTaxDiscre=
pancy</span> &gt; 10.00)</td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd">15.2</td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd">RecurringInvoiceIsValid</td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd">true/false</td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Returns false if the invoice source is "Recurring" and one or more docum=
ent configuration errors exist (ex: missing required field). Returns true f=
or all other source types, or if there are no document configuration errors=
 on a recurring invoice.<br>
(Example usage: Document.RecurringInvoiceIsValid =3D=3D false)</p></td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd">15.1</td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd">HasNonConfiguredMiscFees</td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd">true/false</td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Returns true if there are any miscellaneous fees on the invoice that are=
 not set up on the AP Configuration page. Returns false if all of the fees =
saved to the document have been configured.<br>
(Example usage: Document.HasNonConfiguredMiscFees =3D=3D true</p></td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd">16.1</td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd">IsInvoiceOwnerBlank</td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd">true/false</td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Returns true if the invoice owner is blank/empty or null. Returns false =
if the invoice has an owner.</p>
<p>(Exmaple usage: Document.IsInvoiceOwnerBlank =3D=3D true)</p></td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd">16.2</td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">HasDiscount</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">true/false</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">(Document.HasDiscount=3D true) will evaluate to =
true when a supplier level or a line level discount is present anywhere on =
the document.</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">17.2</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">X</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd">HasTradeIn</td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd">true/false</td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd">(Document.HasTradeIn =3D true) wil=
l evaluate to true when any line item in the invoice is a product type =3D =
TradeIn. TradeIn items have a negative unit price.</td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd">17.1</td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd">X</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd">Has Evaluated Receipt Settlement P=
O</td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd">true/false</td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><span>Will return TRUE if the PO h=
as the Evaluated Receipt Settlement field true.</span></td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd">17.2</td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd">X</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd">Document.ContractItemQuantityExcee=
ded</td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd">true/false</td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd">Returns true if at least one Contr=
act Non-Catalog Item line on the document contains a quantity that exceeds =
the allowable Contracted Quantity for that item, when considering the curre=
nt Total Purchased Quantity of the item added to the proposed line quantity=
, if and only if the item is marked to "Enforce Contracted Quantity". Contr=
acted Quantity, Total Purchased Quantity, and Enforce Contracted Quantity a=
re all new 21.2 attributes on Contract Non-Catalog Items.</td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd">21.2</td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><span data-colorid=3D"utuc8iaasa">=
Document.OutTotalAmountTolerance</span></td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd">true/false</td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Static WF Rule for OCR/DMR invoices that compares the 'Grand Total' tag =
on the XML invoice vs the total of the invoice in the UI.&nbsp; Will return=
 'True' if the difference exceeds the amount configured on the AP Config pa=
ge (see setting - '<strong>Allowed tolerance for difference in Invoice Impo=
rt XML total and the current Invoice Total</strong>').&nbsp;</p>
<p>Example -&nbsp;<strong><span data-colorid=3D"gjs89zcpx5">Document.OutTot=
alAmountTolerance =3D=3D true</span></strong></p></td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd">21.3</td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd">IsBudgetDateRangeClosed</td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd">true/false</td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd">Returns true if any line in the tr=
ansaction is associated with a Budget Date Range that is Closed.</td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd">22.1</td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<pre>Document.IsAutoPaymentAllowed</pre></td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd">true/false</td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Returns true if org setting<strong> 'Enable JAGGAER Pay Automation Proce=
ss'</strong> is true and Invoice targets a registered supplier.</p><span cl=
ass=3D"legacy-color-text-inverse">difference exceeds the amountomation Proc=
ess' is true and Invoice has registered supplier (i.e., not a manual suppli=
er).</span></td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd">22.3</td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><span>Has Inactive Owner</span></t=
d>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd">true/false</td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd">(Document.HasInactiveOwner =3D tru=
e<span>) will evaluate to true when the requisition owner is Inactive</span=
></td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd">22.3</td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd">X</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
