<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Document.IsRejectedFlag&nbsp;</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">true/false&nbsp;</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">&nbsp;The org has the option of checking a suppl=
ier to see if this flag is set and allowing it to sit in a step based on th=
at value.&nbsp; "IIsRejectedFlag" checks the customer relationship to deter=
mine the value, true means that they have rejected the supplier.&nbsp; ex. =
Document.isRejectedFlag=3Dtrue</td>
