<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>wfMustHaveAwardedSupplierResponse</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Workflow <strong>attribute </strong>that can be =
placed on a workflow step in evaluations workflow that will prevent someone=
 from approving it out of that step without having a response marked as awa=
rded. When clicking approve in a step where the new attribute is present, t=
he user should not be allowed to approve the event and should receive an er=
ror message using the red bubble. Error Message Text: An awarded response i=
s required to approve this sourcing event.
<pre>&lt;Attribute name=3D"wfMustHaveAwardedSupplierResponse"&gt;
          &lt;AttrValue lang=3D"default"&gt;true&lt;/AttrValue&gt;
    &lt;/Attribute&gt;</pre></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">&nbsp;14.2</td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
