<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd">wfMustHaveSavedScenario</td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><span>Workflow </span> <strong>att=
ribute </strong> <span>that can be placed on a workflow step in evaluation =
workflow that will prevent someone from approving it out of that step witho=
ut having a saved scenario. When clicking approve in a step where the new a=
ttribute is present, the user should not be allowed to approve the event an=
d should receive an error message using the red bubble. Error Message Text:=
 A saved scenario is required to approve this sourcing event.</span></td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd">14.3</td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd">Document.<span class=3D"legacy-col=
or-text-default">IsSupplierWithoutERP</span></td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd">True/False</td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd">Will return true if any of the awa=
rded suppliers do not have an ERP ID.</td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd">15.1</td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><br></p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
