<h2 style=3D"text-align: left;" id=3D"WorkflowObjects-SupplierRelated"><str=
ong>Supplier Related<br></strong></h2>
<h3 style=3D"text-align: left;" id=3D"WorkflowObjects-Supplier">Supplier</h=
3>
<p>(All attributes will be blank if an ad-hoc supplier was entered via the =
non-catalog form. More attributes are available besides the ones below)&nbs=
p;</p>
<p><strong>As part of 13.3 these attributes have been exposed to Supplier R=
egistration Workflow</strong></p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table class=3D"wrapped confluenceTable" style=3D"text-align: left;">
<colgroup>
<col>
<col>
<col>
<col>
<col>
</colgroup>
<tbody>
<tr>
