<p>12.1</p></td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>ofacCheckPassed</p></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>true/false</p></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Will trigger based on whether the Supplier is an Ofac match (Ex: Supplie=
r.ofacCheckPassed=3D=3Dfalse). This object can be used in Supplier Registra=
tion, Requisition, Purchase Order and Invoice Workflow</p></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>13.3</p></td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>HasExpiredInsurance</p></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>true/false</p></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Will return True if the insurance for a supplier has expired and False i=
f the insurance has not expired or does not exist.&nbsp;<br>
Example: Supplier.HasExpiredInsurance=3Dtrue. This object can be used with =
Supplier Registration, Requisition, Purchase Order, Invoice, Fulfillment Wo=
rkflows.</p></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>13.3</p></td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>RegistrationMethod</p></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>String</p></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Supplier Registration Method: "Solicited" =3D warm (invited) registratio=
n, "Unsolicited" =3D cold registration or "UnsolicitedInvoiceMatch" =3D sel=
f registration (AP Only)&nbsp;<br>
Examples:&nbsp;<br>
Supplier.RegistrationMethod=3D"Solicited", Supplier.RegistrationMethod=3D"U=
nsolicitedCold", Supplier.RegistrationMethod=3D"UnsolicitedInvoiceMatch".&n=
bsp;<br>
This object can be used in Supplier Registration, Requisition, Purchase Ord=
er, and Invoice Workflow</p></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>13.3</p></td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">SupplierHasRegistered</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">true/false</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Will return true if it is in any state but NA, N=
one or Invited.</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">14.2</td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p style=3D"text-align: left;"><br></p>
